sejak aku memulai...</font>

45
00:02:25,262 --> 00:02:26,562
<font color="yellow">...investigasi kasus ini.</font>

46
00:02:26,563 --> 00:02:28,497
<font color="yellow">Apa aku harus terus mendengar hal ini?</font>

47
00:02:28,498 --> 00:02:31,934
<font color="yellow">Det. Moo, pelaku kasus Eunhyung-dong
adalah seorang monster.</font>

48
00:02:31,935 --> 00:02:34,837
<font color="yellow">Dia akan melakukan apapun
untuk memprovokasi kita.</font>

49
00:02:34,838 --> 00:02:37,540
<font color="yellow">Dan kemarin, sepertinya pelaku Eunhyung-dong,</font>

50
00:02:37,541 --> 00:02:40,644
<font color="yellow">...datang kerumahku saat aku
sedang diluar.</font>

51
00:02:41,411 --> 00:02:45,148
<font color="yellow">Dia mengambil fotoku bersama Ayahku
yang kami ambil...</font>

52
00:02:45,916 --> 00:02:47,436
<font color="yellow">...tepat sebelum aku menjadi petugas
kepolisian.</font>

53
00:02:48,451 --> 00:02:50,686
<font color="yellow">Apapun itu,</font>

54
00:02:50,687 --> 00:02:52,621
<font color="yellow">aku tahu ini tidak mudah.</font>

55
00:02:52,622 --> 00:02:54,423
<font color="yellow">Namun, dalam situasi seperti ini,</font>

56
00:02:54,424 --> 00:02:56,726
<font color="yellow">kau harus memutuskan dengan bijak.</font>

57
00:02:59,396 --> 00:03:01,064
<font color="yellow">Aku butuh udara segar.</font>

58
00:03:25,388 --> 00:03:26,455
<font color="yellow">Halo?</font>

59
00:03:26,456 --> 00:03:29,659
<font color="yellow">Moo Jin Hyuk. Apa sebaiknya kita
berdua bicara?</font>

60
00:03:29,993 --> 00:03:32,629
<font color="yellow">Tak perlu repot-repot
melacak nomor ini.</font>

61
00:03:32,963 --> 00:03:35,007
<font color="yellow">Aku punya informasi untukmu...</font>

62
00:03:35,031 --> 00:03:37,467
<font color="yellow">...yang lebih berharga daripada
kau harus repot-repot melacak nomor ini.</font>

63
00:03:37,968 --> 00:03:40,804
<font color="yellow">Tak usah basa-basi.</font>

64
00:03:42,205 --> 00:03:43,616
<font color="yellow">Apa sekarang kau bisa?</font>

65
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,984
<font color="yellow">Terus bicara, bajingan.</font>

66
00:03:45,008 --> 00:03:48,411
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin membuat kesepakatan.</font>

67
00:03:52,749 --> 00:03:56,419
<font color="yellow">Bajingan. Kau tidak mengerti?</font>

68
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:59,188
<font color="yellow">Saat aku menangkapmu, kau tamat.</font>

69
00:03:59,189 --> 00:04:01,091
<font color="yellow">Omong kosong apa yang kaubicarakan?</font>

70
00:04:08,732 --> 00:04:12,044
<font color="yellow">Halo, ini CEO MO dari Sungwun Express.</font>

71
00:04:12,068 --> 00:04:15,672
<font color="yellow">Inspektur Kang, apa bisa kita bertemu?</font>

72
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:19,075
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana dia bisa tahu namaku?</font>

73
00:04:19,876 --> 00:04:22,911
<font color="yellow">Aku akan membantumu menangkap
pelaku kasus Eunhyung-dong.</font>

74
00:04:22,912 --> 00:04:26,983
<font color="yellow">Aku juga akan memberikan bukti dari
tindakan ilegal...</font>

75
00:04:27,117 --> 00:04:29,119
<font color="yellow">...yang pernah dia lakukan.</font>

76
00:04:29,419 --> 00:04:30,487
<font color="yellow">Namun,</font>

77
00:04:31,121 --> 00:04:32,721
<font color="yellow">syaratnya kau harus membebaskanku.</font>

78
00:04:32,722 --> 00:04:33,889
<font color="yellow">Kalau aku menolak?</font>

79
00:04:33,890 --> 00:04:34,924
<font color="yellow">Maka...</font>

80
00:04:35,659 --> 00:04:37,661
<font color="yellow">kau akan hidup...</font>

81
00:04:37,894 --> 00:04:40,630
<font color="yellow">...dalam rasa penasaran dan bertanya-tanya
mengapa isterimu dibunuh.</font>

82
00:04:41,431 --> 00:04:42,432
<font color="yellow">Kenapa...</font>

83
00:04:44,934 --> 00:04:46,603
<font color="yellow">...aku harus memercayaimu?</font>

84
00:04:46,770 --> 00:04:49,606
<font color="yellow">Kau ingat Resor Solhyang?</font>

85
00:04:50,874 --> 00:04:53,777
<font color="yellow">Aku yakin kau ingat karena kau pernah
