86
00:04:53,943 --> 00:04:55,110
<font color="yellow">Ayo bertemu disana.</font>

87
00:04:55,111 --> 00:04:57,914
<font color="yellow">Apa? Kau percaya denganku sekarang?</font>

88
00:04:58,348 --> 00:04:59,449
<font color="yellow">Apa kau bilang?</font>

89
00:05:03,219 --> 00:05:04,254
<font color="yellow">Det. Park.</font>

90
00:05:05,021 --> 00:05:06,255
<font color="yellow">Apa kau memanggil Mo Tae Gu,
Mo Gi Beom,</font>

91
00:05:06,256 --> 00:05:08,390
<font color="yellow">Menteri Kim Joon Tae dan
Direktur Kwon Chang Tae...</font>

92
00:05:08,391 --> 00:05:10,025
<font color="yellow">...sebagai saksi?</font>

93
00:05:10,026 --> 00:05:12,762
<font color="yellow">Ah, itu. Aku baru akan memangil mereka.</font>

94
00:05:13,396 --> 00:05:15,798
<font color="yellow">Namun mereka memiliki kuasa yang kuat.</font>

95
00:05:15,799 --> 00:05:17,166
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak tahu apa mereka
