96
00:05:17,167 --> 00:05:19,868
<font color="yellow">Kau harus memanggil mereka secepatnya.</font>

97
00:05:19,869 --> 00:05:21,404
<font color="yellow">Baik, Bu.</font>

98
00:05:22,939 --> 00:05:24,140
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

99
00:05:24,474 --> 00:05:26,909
<font color="yellow">Dengarkan aku baik-baik, brengsek.</font>

100
00:05:26,910 --> 00:05:30,045
<font color="yellow">Jika kau mencoba membohongiku,</font>

101
00:05:30,046 --> 00:05:32,315
<font color="yellow">aku tidak segan akan membunuhmu.</font>

102
00:05:32,949 --> 00:05:33,917
<font color="yellow">Mengerti?</font>

103
