<font color="yellow">Dia meneleponku sendiri...</font>

122
00:06:34,711 --> 00:06:37,446
<font color="yellow">...yang berarti dia tidak
punya pilihan lain.</font>

123
00:06:37,447 --> 00:06:40,716
<font color="yellow">Detektif, dia mungkin saja bukan
pelaku Eunhyung-dong,</font>

124
00:06:40,717 --> 00:06:42,419
<font color="yellow">namun dia tetap berbahaya.</font>

125
00:06:42,619 --> 00:06:46,456
<font color="yellow">Apa kau tetap percaya dia
akan memegang kata-katanya?</font>

126
00:06:46,723 --> 00:06:49,425
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak kesana karena memercayainya,
