138
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:48,617
<font color="yellow">Maaf? Apa maksudmu?</font>

139
00:07:48,618 --> 00:07:50,686
<font color="yellow">Nam Sang Tae memintanya untuk bertemu.</font>

140
00:07:50,687 --> 00:07:53,522
<font color="yellow">Dia meminta Det. Moo datang sendiri
