<font color="yellow">- Kau ingat Resor Solhyang?
- Resor Solhyang.</font>

150
00:08:25,221 --> 00:08:26,389
<font color="yellow">Resor Solhyang...</font>

151
00:08:28,024 --> 00:08:31,127
<font color="yellow">Det. Shim, kau bisa mencari tahu
alamat Resor Solhyang?</font>

